{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Anime Bergaya Ghibli: Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower","content":"<p>Hai buat kamu para pecinta anime, pernah nonton The Secret World of Arrietty? Atau When Marnie Was There? Penah nonton? Wah kalau kamu pernah nonton kedua anime diatas, bisa dipastikan kamu pasti penonton setia anime keluaran Ghibli! Dan pastinya kamu ga akan mau ketinggalan anime yang satu ini.</p>\n<p>Eitss, tunggu dulu, anime yang bakal kita bahas bukan dari Studio Ghibli, melainkan Studio Ponoc. Nah, Anime Mary and The Witch’s Flower merupakan anime pertama produksi Studio Ponoc. Namun, yang menjadi perbincangan dari anime ini adalah, <em>art</em> dan <em>stylenya</em> mirip sekali dengan Ghibli!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8583\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8583\" data-attachment-id=\"8583\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/6-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster Official Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: catsuka.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster Official Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: catsuka.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8583\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"Poster Official Mary and The Witch's Flower (Sumber: catsuka.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8583\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Official Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: catsuka.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kemiripan anime Studio Ponoc dan Ghibli terlihat dari<em> trailer</em> film terbarunya, Menurut penggemar Ghibli, konsep Mary and The Witch’s Flower merupakan gabungan dari beberapa anime terkenal Ghibli seperti Spirited Away, Howl’s Moving Castle, Kiki Delivery Service dan Ponyo.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8575\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8575\" data-attachment-id=\"8575\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/3-57/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cuplikan dari scene Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Tuh, mirip kan? (Sumber: nerdist.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cuplikan dari scene Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Tuh, mirip kan? (Sumber: nerdist.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8575\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-11.jpg\" alt=\"Cuplikan dari scene Mary and The Witch's Flower. Tuh, mirip kan? (Sumber: nerdist.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8575\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cuplikan dari scene Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Tuh, mirip kan? (Sumber: nerdist.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8573\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8573\" data-attachment-id=\"8573\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/2-46/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Salah satu scene dari Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Ghibli banget deh! (Sumber: nerdist.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Salah satu scene dari Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Ghibli banget deh! (Sumber: nerdist.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8573\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-7.jpg\" alt=\"Salah satu scene dari Mary and The Witch's Flower. Ghibli banget deh! (Sumber: nerdist.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8573\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salah satu scene dari Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower. Ghibli banget deh! (Sumber: nerdist.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sebenarnya hal ini tidak mengherankan, mengingat animator Studio Ponoc merupakan <em>creator-creator</em> yang pernah bekerjasama dengan Hayao Miyazaki, pendiri Studio Ghibli. Bahkan director dari film Mary and the Witch’s Flower, Hiromasa Yonebayashi, pernah menggarap beberapa film studio Ghibli antara lain, The Secret World of Arrietty dan When Marnie was There.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8571\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8571\" data-attachment-id=\"8571\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/1-57/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hiromasa Yonebayashi selaku director dari anime pertama keluaran Studio Ponoc, Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: trespassmag.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hiromasa Yonebayashi selaku director dari anime pertama keluaran Studio Ponoc, Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: trespassmag.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8571\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-11.jpg\" alt=\"Hiromasa Yonebayashi selaku director dari anime pertama keluaran Studio Ponoc, Mary and The Witch's Flower (Sumber: trespassmag.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8571\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hiromasa Yonebayashi selaku director dari anime pertama keluaran Studio Ponoc, Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower (Sumber: trespassmag.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Oya, untuk informasi tambahan, nama ‘Ponoc’ merupakan terjemahan yang bahasa Serbo-Croation, yang berarti <em>Midnight</em>, dan didefinisikan sebagai permulaan yang baru. Kabarnya, saat anime ini usai dibuat, Director Hiromasa Yonebayashi sempat memperlihatkan anime ini kepada Hayao Miyazaki. Namun, tanpa perlu melihatnya, Hayao Miyazaki pun sudah memuji anime tersebut. Padahal Hayao Miyazaki terkenal akan pelit pujian dan sosok yang sangat <em>strict</em>. Banyak yang menganggap bahwa sikap Hayao Miyazaki ini dikarenakan beliau sangat mempercayai Hiromasa Yonebayashi yang pernah bekerja dengannya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8581\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8581\" data-attachment-id=\"8581\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/5-43/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hayao Miyazaki (Sumber: japantimes.co.jp)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hayao Miyazaki (Sumber: japantimes.co.jp)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8581\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-7.jpg\" alt=\"Hayao Miyazaki (Sumber: japantimes.co.jp)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8581\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hayao Miyazaki (Sumber: japantimes.co.jp)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sebelumnya perlu diingat, bahwa saat bekerja di studio Ghibli, Hiromasa Yonebayashi terbilang sukses dengan keberhasilan kedua anime yang digarapnya. Bahkan When Marnie Was There dan The Secret World of Arriety merupakan anime keluaran Ghibli pertama yang sukses yang bukan diproduksi oleh Hayao Miyazaki.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8585\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8585\" data-attachment-id=\"8585\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-bergaya-ghibli-mary-witchs-flower/attachment/7-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/7-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The Secret World of Arrietty (Sumber: allgeektomeblog)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;The Secret World of Arrietty (Sumber: allgeektomeblog)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/7-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/7-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8585\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/7-2.jpg\" alt=\"The Secret World of Arrietty (Sumber: allgeektomeblog)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8585\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Secret World of Arrietty (Sumber: allgeektomeblog)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kesamaan lainnya, juga terlihat dari potrait karakter utamanya yang terlihat tegar, kuat, dan dapat dengan mudah relate dengan penonton. Selain itu, komposer <em>soundtrack</em> Mary and the Witch’s Flower merupakan komposer yang pernah menangani <em>soundtrack</em> When Marnie was There. Tentunya hal ini juga yang ditunggu-tunggu, mengingat hingga saat ini soundtrack When Marnie Was There masih digemari dan menjadi favorit penggemarnya.</p>\n<p>Dan terdapat dua perdebatan yang bertolak belakang, beberapa ada yang tidak suka dengan kemiripan anime ini dengan studio Ghibli, namun sebagian menganggap hal ini merupakan kabar baik. Karena dengan banyaknya film-film bernuansa Ghibli, akan menambah bahan tontonan, apalagi produksi anime yang biasanya memakan waktu lama, membuat fans Ghibli harus menunggu beberapa tahun lagi untuk film terbarunya.</p>\n<p>Penasaran bagaimana <em>trailer</em> dari anime Mary and The Witch&#8217;s Flower? Berikut <em>trailer-</em>nya :</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cm0YYNgNr7A\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Nah, buat bro sis yang ga sabar pengen nonton, sayangnya anime ini baru akan tayang 8 Juli 2017 nanti di bioskop-bioskop Jepang. huhu.</p>\n<p>Menurut bro sis gimana? Mirip atau tidak? Yay or nay?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"301be674-38a9-5940-88a2-f7440f858299"}}}